title: Ep. - 220 - KATE CHASTAIN FROM BELOW DECK
description:
Kate Chastain from Below Deck on Bravo discusses this season of the show, what makes a nightmare charter guest, what happens off camera with other cast members, and dressing up as Dolly Parton and kenny Rogers with Captain Lee. 

 

Melissa Rycroft Strickland from Dallas Cowboys Cheerleaders: Making the Team and co-host of Logistically Irrational Podcast reviews 'Love After Lockup: Life After Lockup' on WEtv revolves around shocking stories of couples who fall in love despite their partners having been behind bars.
